Please join us on Saturday at 4:00 p.m. and walk a lap with Pal and I at Oakes Park in Niagara Falls at the Heaters Heroes Run for the children. Bring your dog out and walk a lap with Russell Langendoen to show your support. Russell suffers from leukemia, but from what I hear about him, he is one strong little boy.
